data.text:
These Interior Department maps are among the best maps of Arizona. In this version of the well drawn map the land forms are emphasized and the forests and Indian Reservations are colored brightly. It was done by I.P. Berthrong who was an excellent cartographer.

Very good. Image size is 20.25 x 16.5, substantial color.
